不錯的地方，但對於卡拉 OK 來說太優雅了。感覺就像一家飯店，四面八方都有工作人員。休息室設備齊全，但有點局促，因為當有人想離開椅子時，每個人都參與其中，必須移動或將腳放在沙發上才能讓他們出去。當我們點了 3 瓶香檳時，我們看到 3 個裝扮成希臘女神的女人跳起了可笑的舞蹈，但每次都讓她們感到非常不舒服。最大的客廳設有衛浴，非常實用。我們可以玩弄客廳的燈光和氣氛。歌曲比我們預期的要少得多，而且計算機上有相當多的目錄，但都是空的……英語翻譯選項也可用，但不能翻譯任何內容，所以你只能用中文。

音質很好，我們仍然度過了一個美好的夜晚，因為我們和朋友在一起，但下次我會去另一家卡拉 OK。

Good places, but it is too elegant for karaoke.It feels like a restaurant, with staff in all directions.The lounge is complete, but it is a bit cramped, because when someone wants to leave the chair, everyone is involved and must move or put their feet on the sofa to let them go out.When we ordered 3 bottles of champagne, we saw 3 women dressed as the Greek goddess danced, but every time they felt very uncomfortable.The largest living room is equipped with bathroom, which is very practical.We can play with the lights and atmosphere of the living room.The songs are much less than we expect, and there are quite a lot of directory on the computer, but they are all empty ... English translation options are also available, but they cannot translate any content, so you can only use Chinese.
The waiter who came to order food does not care about you singing, nor does you care that you must read the lyrics on the screen.They stood in the middle of everything, thinking that they were transparent, and maybe they could put the order on the side of the table.
The sound quality is very good, we still have a beautiful night, because we are with friends, but next time I will go to another karaoke.
